{"tid":2030873,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"學唔到林鄭 - 不敵網民惡評　《雙層公寓》22歲木村花自殺身亡","createTime":"2020-05-23T04:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T11:36:30.000Z","uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab50f8e104357c44f514304e59c51e9c3a8121e","tid":2030873,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:58:18.000Z","msg":"如果佢柒婆一半既堅定同面皮  死既就係佢D敵人  可惜可惜<br />\n<br />\n不敵網民惡評 《雙層公寓》22歲木村花自殺身亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200523/bkn-20200523112340690-0523_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200523%2Fbkn-20200523112340690-0523_00862_001.html&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CEn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=550bb440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200523/bkn-20200523112340690-0523_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200523/photo/bkn-20200523112340690-0523_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200523124907\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200523%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200523112340690-0523_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200523124907&h=419069f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n22歲日本女摔角手木村花，去年10月加入真人騷配對節目《雙層公寓》（Terrace House Tokyo 2019-2020）成為住客後受到注目，卻因倔強性格，在節目中屢與拍檔發生爭執，因而不少惹來網民評擊。<br />\n今日凌晨，木村花疑難忍網上惡意批評，在社交網上載多張血淋淋的𠝹手照，透露收到不少鬧她「噁心」又叫她「去死」、「消失」的留言，她自嘲是「不被人愛的人生」，感謝誕下她的母親，但其後留言消失，她又在即時動態向愛貓講再見。網民擔心她情緒不穩。木村花所屬事務所Stardom官網，今日中午向傳媒證實其離世消息，表示會與其家人商討有關辦理其身後事。"},{"pid":"1913a003b36208ebc14f594c18ce37624b2aa3c3","tid":2030873,"uid":51840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ab50f8e104357c44f514304e59c51e9c3a8121e","tid":2030873,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:58:18.000Z","msg":"如果佢柒婆一半既堅定同面皮  死既就係佢D敵人  可惜可惜<br />\n<br />\n不敵網民惡評 《雙層公寓》22歲木村花自殺身亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200523/bkn-20200523112340690-0523_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200523%2Fbkn-20200523112340690-0523_00862_001.html&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CEn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=550bb440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200523/bkn-20200523112340690-0523_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200523/photo/bkn-20200523112340690-0523_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200523124907\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200523%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200523112340690-0523_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200523124907&h=419069f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n22歲日本女摔角手木村花，去年10月加入真人騷配對節目《雙層公寓》（Terrace House Tokyo 2019-2020）成為住客後受到注目，卻因倔強性格，在節目中屢與拍檔發生爭執，因而不少惹來網民評擊。<br />\n今日凌晨，木村花疑難忍網上惡意批評，在社交網上載多張血淋淋的𠝹手照，透露收到不少鬧她「噁心」又叫她「去死」、「消失」的留言，她自嘲是「不被人愛的人生」，感謝誕下她的母親，但其後留言消失，她又在即時動態向愛貓講再見。網民擔心她情緒不穩。木村花所屬事務所Stardom官網，今日中午向傳媒證實其離世消息，表示會與其家人商討有關辦理其身後事。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:02:48.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ec2a38b8fca91750612619245bdb22f3247093","tid":2030873,"uid":179409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:04:26.000Z","msg":"太睇唔開<br />\n鬧佢嘅人都係趁熱鬧發牙痕<br />\n鬧完自己爽完<br />\n轉頭就唔記得鬧過佢"},{"pid":"48fb982158d150e79ba377cfddc4af2e85855ea6","tid":2030873,"uid":113984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:11:22.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"41f82b7fd1c5a9e362a4454c8484048299b35266","tid":2030873,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:20:29.000Z","msg":"唔夠無恥 RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db993116913214db9527f762727f0a8885149c2e","tid":2030873,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1